sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant App as App.tsx
    participant WS as WebSocket
    participant API as /generate-minutes
    participant LLM as Local LLM Service

    User->>App: Click 'End Meeting & Generate Minutes'
    App->>WS: Close Connection (Stop Transcription)
    App->>App: Set isGenerating = true
    App->>API: POST /generate-minutes { transcript }
    
    activate API
    API->>LLM: Prompt Context + Transcript
    activate LLM
    LLM-->>API: Generated Minutes (Markdown)
    deactivate LLM
    API-->>App: Return JSON { minutes/points }
    deactivate API

    App->>App: Set minutes state
    App->>App: Update SummaryPanel
    App->>User: Display Meeting Minutes
